reviewText: It was entertaining to see the old biker movies .

don't waste your money on this so called "biker triple feature". wild ride isn't even a biker movie. jack starred in it but only motorcycle in whole movie was a motorcycle cop he ran off road. rebel rousers is legit. biker Babylon maybe had a third of the documentary about a motorcycle gang. the rest was protest of the viet nam war in Washington d.c.
EXCELLENT MOVIE. WILL BE ENJOYED BY ALL.

I expected a little more from Jack Nicholson, Rebel Rousers was a real stinker. The second movie Wild Ride is a Black and White flick and boring as it could be, and the third BS movie was just a documentary and more about Vietnam than about bikers, it was awful, DO NO BUY.
Horrible crap. Fun to see Nicholson as a child actor.

The package says biker triple feature, however the movie The Wild Ride is not a biker movie. The closest thing to bikers in it are a couple motorcycle cops. I do like the movie The Rebel Rousers and recommend this set as a inexpensive way to get that movie as opposed to buying it by itself which will cost more than this set.
It must have cost a whole $25 budget to make all 3 films. But the seller is great. Seeing Jack Nicholson as a 20's something young actor in black and white was cool though.
I like them old movies. He'll ride is awesome
THESE 3 MOVIES ARE REALLY BAD-THOUGHT THEY WOULD BE B MOVIES, BUT I GOT F- IN THE TRASH IT GOES.
it was old but really good classic biker movie
